s that take place at the airport. Sheung-wai keeps in touch with his ex-wife Cheung Yeuk-ling, Metro Harbour Airlines Airport Supervisor. Actually, they still think of each other after their divorce. The duo’s relationship is rekindled when airline captain Kwok Kai-kwong and flight attendant Ko Nga-man turn up.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"243236","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2025-01-10T10:34:27.000Z","cast":["Kenneth Ma Kwok-Ming","Sisley Choi Si-Pui","Samantha Ko","Hồng Vĩnh Thành","Trần Hào","Chu Mẫn Hãn","Lưu Dĩnh Tuyền","Quách Bách Nghiên","Đới Tổ Nghi","Ngô Vĩ Hào","Tsui Wing","Tiffany Fabienne Kwan"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Kenneth Ma Kwok-Ming","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kenneth Ma Kwok-Ming","tmdb_id":1232198,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6DejZHB8htcmosNwuOGJeDUgfJr.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1232198"},{"name":"Sisley Choi Si-Pui","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Sisley Choi Si-Pui","tmdb_id":1545561,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kMoFQdV3Do1kIuDMq2dYOYNrMZ2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1545561"},{"name":"Samantha Ko","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Samantha Ko","tmdb_id":1173598,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/trFirFO6af8zjdwbVNQI4YMpKf6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1173598"},{"name":"Hồng Vĩnh Thành","name_vi":"Hồng Vĩnh Thành","name_original":"Tony Hung","tmdb_id":2214358,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vsJtcHg5IIOmZTIHrhntjjwZ5zl.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2214358"},{"name":"Trần Hào","name_vi":"Trần Hào","name_original":"Moses Chan Ho","tmdb_id":551869,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gvZcLkr1GMPajHROKd7rqzYWQbj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/551869"},{"name":"Chu Mẫn Hãn","name_vi":"Chu Mẫn Hãn","name_original":"Brian Chu","tmdb_id":2705751,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lZzBMzKAN8s9KNY2fXJ21xDgNeu.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.th